#### TransitionToNextRoom (Function)
**Graph:** BP_DoorActor > TransitionToNextRoom
 
**Logic:**
1. **Get All Actors Of Class**
   - Actor Class: BP_DungeonGenerator
   - Out Actors → **GET** [0] (first element)
2. **Is Valid** (Input Object: BP_DungeonGenerator reference)
   - **Is Valid** → **On Room Completed** (Target: BP_DungeonGenerator)
     → **Print String** — `"Notifying generator"` *(Development Only)*
   - **Is Not Valid** → **Print String** — `"ERROR: No generator found"` *(Development Only)*
     → **Return Node**
 
> Finds the BP_DungeonGenerator in the level and calls On Room Completed on it. Prints an error and exits early if no generator is found.
 
